public class ServernodeIOStatus
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable

ServernodeIOStatus represents the status of IO. io_rate means how busy io is, that's to say, how often read/write happens in a specified time slot.
